query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('arm',
'docker-compose',
'fragment',
'global-variables',
'imageview',
'include',
'jenkins-pipeline',
'msbuild',
'runtime',
'sbt',
'socket.io',
'xml-parsing');
